sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Container, TextField, Button, Typography, Link, Grid, Box, Paper, Avatar } from '@mui/material'; import { Google as GoogleIcon, Facebook as FacebookIcon, Person as PersonIcon, Lock as LockIcon } from '@mui/icons-material'; import { styled } from '@mui/system'; const BackgroundBox = styled(Box)(({ theme }) => ({ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'row', height: '100vh', alignItems: 'center', justifyContent: 'center', backgroundColor: '#f5f5f5', })); const FormBox = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({ padding: theme.spacing(4), display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'column', alignItems: 'center', width: '100%', maxWidth: '400px', boxShadow: '0px 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1)', borderRadius: '12px', })); const InputBox = styled(Box)(({ theme }) => ({ display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', backgroundColor: '#e0f7fa', borderRadius: '8px', marginBottom: theme.spacing(2), })); const StyledTextField = styled(TextField)(({ theme }) => ({ '& .MuiInputBase-input': { padding: '10px 12px', }, })); const IconWrapper = styled(Box)(({ theme }) => ({ padding: theme.spacing(1), })); const Login = () => { return ( Login and start bulking right now! Forgot your password? Login with Others Not a member? Register now ); } export default Login;
